In order to fix a reasonable value for $M_0$, we can now assume
that, for sufficiently large ADM mass, the standard Hawking relation
holds \cite{hawking},
\begin{eqnarray}
{\dot M}\sim -n_{\rm B}\,K\,{\ell_p^2\over M^2}
\ ,
\label{LH}
\end{eqnarray}
